CSS:
----
Cascading style sheets 
CSS using for styling web pages 
CSS applied on top of html 

CSS can be applied on top of html in 3 diff ways 

1. inline CSS  : element related CSS
2. internal CSS : page related css 
3. external CSS : app related CSS 

colors 
background color 
font properties 
text properties 

selectors 
positions 
box model 

selectors 
------------
selector is selecting some  thing from html to css 

selectors are multiple types 
1. tag selector 
2. class selector 
3. id selector 
4. group selector 
5. universal selector 
6. even selector 
7. odd selector 


box model 
------------
width :   horizontal space 
height : vertical space 
padding : inner space 
margin : outer space 
border : simple decoration (border-width,border-color,border-style)
outline : extra decoration on top of border 
(outline-width,outline-color,outline-style)

Note: in html every element is a rectangular box 
